<div class="main-content">

    <h1>Staff Privacy Policy for Dental Management System</h1>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle personal information provided by staff using our Dental Management System. Your privacy is a priority, and we ensure your data is securely managed and protected.</p>

    <h2>Information Collected</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Details:</strong> Name, address, contact details, emergency contact information.</li>
        <li><strong>Employment Data:</strong> Job titles, work schedules, employee ID, training, and performance records.</li>
        <li><strong>System Access Data:</strong> Login credentials, usage logs, and security audit trails.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Purpose of Information Collection</h2>
    <p>We use staff information to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Manage staff accounts and permissions.</li>
        <li>Maintain accurate employment records.</li>
        <li>Ensure security and compliance with policies.</li>
        <li>Facilitate payroll and benefit management.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Information Disclosure</h2>
    <p>Staff information will remain confidential and will not be shared externally except under the following conditions:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>With authorized third-party service providers (e.g., payroll, benefits administration).</li>
        <li>When required by law or legal processes.</li>
        <li>With explicit staff consent.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Security Measures</h2>
    <p>We implement strong security controls to prevent unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure of your information, including encryption, secure authentication, and regular security audits.</p>

    <h2>Retention of Information</h2>
    <p>Personal and employment-related data is retained only for as long as required for employment purposes or as mandated by law.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access and review your personal data.</li>
        <li>Request corrections to your data.</li>
        <li>Request deletion or restriction of your data, subject to applicable laws and policies.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Policy Updates</h2>
    <p>This policy may be updated periodically. Staff will be notified of significant changes through email or system notifications.</p>

    <h2>Contact Information</h2>
    <p>For questions or concerns regarding this policy, please contact us at:</p>
    <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong> DentalClinic@gmail.com<br>
        <strong>Phone:</strong> 083-2239325<br>
        <strong>Address:</strong> Dental Clinic, Letterkenny
    </p>

    <hr>
    <p><em>Effective Date: 2025</em></p>

</div>